headline: How Investors Are Reacting To Steel Dynamics (STLD) Earnings Outlook And Fresh Fortune Accolade
summary: Steel Dynamics, Inc. is set to report its fourth-quarter earnings on January 26, 2026, with analysts expecting higher earnings and revenue than the prior year, while recent commentary has highlighted potential benefits from tariffs on foreign steel. At the same time, Fortune named Steel Dynamics one of the World's Most Admired Companies for the ninth consecutive year, underscoring external recognition of its innovation, people management, and product quality. headline: Big Tech earnings, Fed meeting feature as markets end January with busiest week of Q1: What to watch
summary: As geopolitical tensions simmer in the background, Big Tech earnings and the January Fed meeting take center stage this week.
